{
  "stem": "1292.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the night, she did have a terrible urge, because diarrhea always associated with this complaint.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she used, what I understand, any vessel what was available.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she was self-conscious of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And being so delirious, she didn't want to take it out to the latrine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But being so feverish, I remember, she spilled some of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember, she spilled over my legs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what can be more contagious than the feces of typhoid fever, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did not get it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember, I washed myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, there was latrines.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They was much better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could keep cleaner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was latrines to wash yourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What was the general feeling there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Did you feel that you were safe now?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Generally feeling there-- and I would like to-- I did see Schindler only from the distance.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a good-looking man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he never did display any aggressiveness towards people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was going, even if the German was there, he wasn't smiling and waving.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was just walking, friendly expression, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I remember very vividly Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Schindler.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somehow, I did see her several time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this girl, who did have the typhoid fever-- who, by the way, did not survive-- but she said-- she express always, before she dies, she wants to have a glass lamp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What she said, a lamp of white wine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I heard, through Mrs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Schindler, she got it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She die-- she die.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but I remember Mrs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schindler always with a little basket covered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was giving whatever she could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She contribute, I think, quite a bit to our diet.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
